{"id":721,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":721,"title":"Isaiah 19","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 19"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord will smite and destroy Egypt—Finally He will heal her, and Egypt and Assyria will be blessed with Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.1","order":"02.24.019.46670"},["b","1"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"burden"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Egypt"],". Behold, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"rideth upon a swift",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"cloud"],", and shall come into Egypt: and the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"idols"],"of Egypt shall be moved at his presence, and the heart of Egypt shall melt in the midst of it."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.2","order":"02.24.019.46671"},["b","2"],"And I will set the Egyptians against the Egyptians: and they shall fight every one against his brother, and every one against his neighbour; city against city,",["i","and"],"kingdom against kingdom."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.3","order":"02.24.019.46672"},["b","3"],"And the spirit of Egypt shall fail in the midst thereof; and I will destroy the counsel thereof: and they shall seek to the idols, and to the charmers, and to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"them"],"that have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"familiar spirits"],", and to the wizards."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.4","order":"02.24.019.46673"},["b","4"],"And the Egyptians will I give over into the hand of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"a"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"cruel"],"lord; and a fierce king shall rule over them, saith the Lord, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.5","order":"02.24.019.46674"},["b","5"],"And the waters shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"fail"],"from the sea, and the river shall be wasted and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"dried"],"up."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.6","order":"02.24.019.46675"},["b","6"],"And they shall turn the rivers far away;",["i","and"],"the brooks of defence shall be emptied and dried up: the reeds and flags shall wither."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.7","order":"02.24.019.46676"},["b","7"],"The paper reeds by the brooks, by the mouth of the brooks, and every thing sown by the brooks, shall wither, be driven away, and be no",["i","more."]],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.8","order":"02.24.019.46677"},["b","8"],"The fishers also shall mourn, and all they that cast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"angle"],"into the brooks shall lament, and they that spread nets upon the waters shall languish."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.9","order":"02.24.019.46678"},["b","9"],"Moreover they that work in fine flax, and they that weave",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"networks"],", shall be confounded."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.10","order":"02.24.019.46679"},["b","10"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"they shall be broken"],"in the purposes thereof, all that make sluices",["i","and"],"ponds for fish."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.11","order":"02.24.019.46680"},["b","11"],"¶Surely the princes of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Zoan"],["i","are"],"fools, the counsel of the wise counsellors of Pharaoh is become brutish: how say ye unto Pharaoh, I",["i","am"],"the son of the wise, the son of ancient kings?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.12","order":"02.24.019.46681"},["b","12"],"Where",["i","are"],"they? where",["i","are"],"thy wise",["i","men?"],"and let them tell thee now, and let them know what the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts hath purposed upon Egypt."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.13","order":"02.24.019.46682"},["b","13"],"The princes of Zoan are become fools, the princes of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Noph"],"are deceived; they have also seduced Egypt,",["i","even they that are"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"stay"],"of the tribes thereof."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.14","order":"02.24.019.46683"},["b","14"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath mingled a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"perverse"],"spirit in the midst thereof: and they have caused Egypt to err in every work thereof, as a drunken",["i","man"],"staggereth in his vomit."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.15","order":"02.24.019.46684"},["b","15"],"Neither shall there be",["i","any"],"work for Egypt, which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"the"],"head or tail, branch or rush, may do."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.16","order":"02.24.019.46685"},["b","16"],"In that day shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Egypt"],"be like unto women: and it shall be afraid and fear because of the shaking of the hand of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, which he shaketh over it."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.17","order":"02.24.019.46686"},["b","17"],"And the land of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Judah"],"shall be a terror unto Egypt, every one that maketh mention thereof shall be afraid in himself, because of the counsel of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, which he hath determined against it."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.18","order":"02.24.019.46687"},["b","18"],"¶In that day shall five cities in the land of Egypt speak the language of Canaan, and swear to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; one shall be called, The city of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"destruction"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.19","order":"02.24.019.46688"},["b","19"],"In that day shall there be an altar to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"in the midst of the land of Egypt, and a pillar at the border thereof to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.20","order":"02.24.019.46689"},["b","20"],"And it shall be for a sign and for a witness unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts in the land of Egypt: for they shall cry unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"because of the oppressors, and he shall send them a saviour, and a great one, and he shall deliver them."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.21","order":"02.24.019.46690"},["b","21"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall be known to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"Egypt"],", and the Egyptians shall know the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"in that day, and shall do sacrifice and oblation; yea, they shall vow a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"vow"],"unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and perform",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.22","order":"02.24.019.46691"},["b","22"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall smite Egypt: he shall smite and heal",["i","it:"],"and they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"return"],["i","even"],"to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and he shall be entreated of them, and shall heal them."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.23","order":"02.24.019.46692"},["b","23"],"¶In that day shall there be a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"highway"],"out of Egypt to Assyria, and the Assyrian shall come into Egypt, and the Egyptian into Assyria, and the Egyptians shall serve with the Assyrians."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.24","order":"02.24.019.46693"},["b","24"],"In that day shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Israel"],"be the third with Egypt and with Assyria,",["i","even"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"blessing"],"in the midst of the land:"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.25","order":"02.24.019.46694"},["b","25"],"Whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts shall bless, saying, Blessed",["i","be"],"Egypt my people, and Assyria the work of my hands, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"Israel"],"mine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"inheritance"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.1a","order":"02.24.019.46695"},["b","1a"],["span.small","IE"],"a message of doom “lifted up” against Egypt."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.1b","order":"02.24.019.46697"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.19"},"Jer. 25:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.13.13-26"},"46:13 (13–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/29.2"},"Ezek. 29:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/31.2"},"31:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/32.2"},"32:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.1c","order":"02.24.019.46699"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/104.3"},"Ps. 104:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.1d","order":"02.24.019.46701"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/12.12"},"Ex. 12:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/43.12"},"Jer. 43:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.3a","order":"02.24.019.46703"},["b","3a"],["span.small","HEB"],"necromancers."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.3b","order":"02.24.019.46705"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorcery"},"TG Sorcery"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.4a","order":"02.24.019.46707"},["b","4a"],["span.small","OR"],"hard masters."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.4b","order":"02.24.019.46709"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/20.4"},"Isa. 20:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.5a","order":"02.24.019.46711"},["b","5a"],["span.small","HEB"],"dry up."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.5b","order":"02.24.019.46713"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/51.36"},"Jer. 51:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/30.12"},"Ezek. 30:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.8a","order":"02.24.019.46715"},["b","8a"],["span.small","OR"],"fish hooks."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.9a","order":"02.24.019.46717"},["b","9a"],["span.small","HEB"],"fine linen."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.10a","order":"02.24.019.46719"},["b","10a"],["span.small","HEB"],"her foundations shall be crushed."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.11a","order":"02.24.019.46721"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/13.22"},"Num. 13:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.13a","order":"02.24.019.46723"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/44.1"},"Jer. 44:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.13b","order":"02.24.019.46725"},["b","13b"],["span.small","IE"],"cornerstones."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.14a","order":"02.24.019.46727"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/22.22.19-23"},"1 Kgs. 22:22 (19–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.15a","order":"02.24.019.46729"},["b","15a"],["span.small","IE"],"the different levels of society."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.16a","order":"02.24.019.46731"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.19"},"Joel 3:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.11"},"Zech. 10:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.17a","order":"02.24.019.46733"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/last-days"},"TG Last Days"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.18a","order":"02.24.019.46735"},["b","18a"],["span.small","HEB"],["span.translit",["span.emphasis","Heres;"]],"possibly “of the sun”; perhaps Heliopolis, one of the oldest cities of the Nile delta."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.21a","order":"02.24.019.46737"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/68.31"},"Ps. 68:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.21b","order":"02.24.019.46739"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vow"},"TG Vow"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.22a","order":"02.24.019.46741"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.23a","order":"02.24.019.46743"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.16"},"Isa. 11:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/21.16"},"2 Ne. 21:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.24a","order":"02.24.019.46745"},["b","24a"],["span.small","IE"],"all three will be allied, with Israel as a blessing in the midst of them."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.24b","order":"02.24.019.46747"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"TG Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.25a","order":"02.24.019.46749"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-remnant-of"},"TG Israel, Remnant of"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.25b","order":"02.24.019.46751"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.2"},"Joel 3:2"],"."]]}
